    <h2>Settings</h2>
    <p>Here you are able to personalise the Met office website to work specifically
       for your needs. Site-wide settings are available for <em>units of measurement</em>
       <span class="map-preferences-description" style="display: none;"> and you can
       set <em>boundaries</em>, <em>place names</em> and <em>map detail</em> in the
       Map preferences section</span>.
    </p>

    <ul id="preference-options">
        <li id="tab-custom-units" class="active">Units of measurement</li>
    </ul>

    <form>
        <fieldset class="custom-units prefs-panel" style="display: block;">
